4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" for those interested in starting a career as a data scientist. This 16-week program requires no previous knowledge and is designed to teach students how to build machine learning models. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, statistics, and various libraries including Pandas and Numpy. Students will learn about supervised and unsupervised learning models, as well as algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The program also focuses on real-life case studies and the use of industry-standard tools. The course is taught by experienced instructors, including Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena. Certificates earned from the course are recognized by multiple organizations. The website for more information is https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop